spans.content: EDWARDS die-cast weatherproof backboxes are perfect for
mounting a variety of EDWARDS signaling appliances such as
bells, horns and sirens.  They are made from die-cast aluminum
and finished at the factory with a baked “Sage Gray” enamel finish
All boxes are shipped complete with a molded neoprene gasket.
They all feature 3/4 inch tapped conduit entries.
– fits  six inch (150mm) and 10 inch (250mm), 325 bells plus
– fits six inch (150mm),  eight inch (203mm) and 10 inch
(250mm) 438 and 439 series bells and CS405 strobes.
